{"tid":1786770,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【聽日石塘咀要人 ─ 香港 對 中國】","createTime":"2019-12-17T11:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T07:04:13.000Z","uid":211043,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"44e61535a6ec79b47cc1117559ce051484f0781e","tid":1786770,"uid":211043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:20:54.000Z","msg":"【東亞盃決賽週放映會 ─ 香港 對 中國】<br />\n<br />\n四年前嘅世界盃外圍賽，港隊將士用命，喺世界盃外圍賽主客兩場賽事逼和中國，創造近年香港足球最輝煌嘅時刻。今年東亞盃，香港同中國再次狹路相逢。賽前兩隊都係兩戰皆北，換言而之，勝出嘅一隊就能夠以較高排名去完成今屆嘅賽事。<br />\n<br />\n為咗等去唔到韓國作客嘅球迷同市民都能夠見證呢場世紀大戰，我哋一班中西區候任區議員會係聽日下晝舉行放映會，直播香港對中國嘅賽事，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：12月18日（三）（聽日）<br />\n開賽時間：下午3時15分<br />\n放映地點：石塘咀山道天橋底（香港大學站B2出口）<br />\n直播賽事：香港對中國<br />\n<br />\n香港呢場一定要贏！You know the reason!"},{"pid":"3c76d4cd2f3b271305313886c4233992d6bc99ac","tid":1786770,"uid":211043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"fa757d9c245d65a91213feb346cf27e103f41478","tid":1786770,"uid":211043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:21:23.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"a5f272d8b5f7c8f063bc19fc3bc1bca1b4b60f6f","tid":1786770,"uid":211043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:21:36.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"43812904d471227c938ca43a23f58a4d97a583c7","tid":1786770,"uid":211043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:21:55.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"ce4bc6fb9b7659ab71bff7d8827e2fcb16921bda","tid":1786770,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:21:57.000Z","msg":"未收工 想睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45489ad8ec33ca3c4ec59af79234ff27cd1d602c","tid":1786770,"uid":211043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:22:06.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"fba64f00efc8215e6bae7fdf7155db74132b1f27","tid":1786770,"uid":211043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:22:19.000Z","m